🔍 Key Features
- Slicers for each month (Jan–Dec) to filter data dynamically
- Cards displaying:
- Total Sale: 308M
- Transactions: 2K
- Total Units Sold: 8K
- Average Sale: 40.6K
  
📈 Visual Insights Include:
- Line Chart: Total Quantity by Month
- Map: Total Sales by City across India
- Funnel: Customer Ratings (1 to 5 stars)
- Area Chart: Total Quantity by Day Name
- Clustered Bar Chart: Total Sale by Brand (Apple, OnePlus, Samsung)
- Pie Chart: Transactions by Payment Method (Credit Card, UPI, Debit Card, Cash)
- Donut Chart: Sum of Units Sold by Brand
- Ribbon Chart: Total Quantity by Brand
